## No Changes Required
Since Vercel Web Analytics is already properly installed and configured according to the latest official documentation, **no additional changes were necessary**. The implementation is correct and ready for use.

## Next Steps for Activation
To start collecting analytics data:
1. Ensure the project is deployed to Vercel
2. Enable Web Analytics in the Vercel dashboard (Project Settings → Analytics)
3. Analytics will automatically start tracking page views and web vitals once enabled in the dashboard

## Notes
- The Analytics component works automatically with Vercel deployments
- No additional configuration or environment variables are required
- The component is tree-shakeable and will not affect bundle size if not used
- Analytics tracking only activates when deployed to Vercel (not in local development)
